These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, white, black, apricot
5 different games are played: go, chess, scrabble, snooker, whist
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, salsa, metal, gospel, blues
 1. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 2. the person who likes white is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the fan of indie is the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of metal##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the person playing chess and the person who likes apricot##2
12. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
13. the person playing whist is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Color   | white     | fuchsia      | black | apricot   | lavender    |
| Game   | snooker  | chess     | go | scrabble | whist  |
| Music-Genre           | salsa | metal      | blues     | gospel   | indie     |

