.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil, aconite, lily, poppy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, red, yellow, aquamarine, amber
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, juice, mirinda, 7up
 1. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 5. the person drinking water is between the person who likes orange and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person who likes yellow is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the person who likes yellow is the person who growsaconite##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Flower         | lily | dahlia | poppy    | daffodil  | aconite    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Color   | amber   | red     | orange    | aquamarine  | yellow     |
| Beverage     | juice    | water | 7up | mirinda | coffee |

