The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
5 different games are played: go, poker, snooker, domino, monopoly
 1. the person who growslily is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person playing go is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
12. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person playing monopoly is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who growsmarigold##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
