.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different games are played: poker, backgammon, chess, scrabble, canasta
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, march, november, october, april
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, water, sprite
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the fan of reggae and the person playing scrabble##2
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Game          | canasta  | chess     | scrabble   | backgammon     | poker |
| Birthday         | april | may    | november  | october | march   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate | water | sprite | mirinda   |

