.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
5 different games are played: poker, monopoly, mah-jongg, whist, go
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks, singing, drawing, reading
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, documentary, time-travel, zombie, action
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
13. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Game   | whist       | go       | poker   | mah-jongg      | monopoly    |
| Hobby       | reading | drawing        | sudoku       | singing       | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre        | action     | documentary        | zombie | scientific        | time-travel  |
| Sport      | volleyball | skateboarding | climbing      | weightlifting | parkour  |

