The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, folk, indie, disco, house
There 5 different types of food: lemon, eggplant, broccoli, plum, kiwi
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person watching zombie movies and the person eating eggplant##2
 7. the person eating broccoli is the fan of house##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
10. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person eating eggplant##2
12. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of disco##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| City      | hannover  | marseilles      | san-francisco   | boston   | liverpool   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | thriller   | sports   | mystery | family     |
