The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, videographer, scientist, librarian, engineer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
5 different pets are kept: pony, horse, rat, lizard, goat
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the modern house is the librarian##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the modern house##1
 6. the librarian is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the scientist is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the musician is on the left of the scientist##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the rat is between the person who's sport is golf and the scientist##2
12. the craftsman house is on the right of the engineer##1
13. the palace house is on the left of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| House    | palace       | craftsman    | townhouse | modern  | cape-cod        |
| Job       | engineer | musician | scientist  | librarian | videographer    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Pet   | lizard       | rat      | goat      | pony | horse  |

