.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, baccarat, aristoff, montecristo, prince
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican, turkish, japanese, indonesian
5 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, guinea-pig, turtle, fish
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the mexican##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is between the turkish and the aristoff-smoker##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the nigerian is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the prince-smoker and the owner of the ferret##2
 7. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the turkish##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is the mexican##1
12. the japanese is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Cigar           | baccarat | aristoff | montecristo | prince    | tiparillo  |
| Nationality   | japanese  | mexican    | nigerian | turkish    | indonesian |
| Pet   | guinea-pig  | ferret        | mouse   | turtle    | fish     |

