.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancerd-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, sprite, fanta, 7up
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, action, crime, family, superhero
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, dancer, chef, security-guard, paramedic
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the paramedic##1
 4. the chef is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching action movies is between the person drinking mirinda and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the teacher and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is dancerd-games##2
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancerd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancerd-games is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | dancerd-games |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | fanta    | juice | 7up | sprite      |
| Movie-Genre           | crime | action    | zombie       | family     | superhero      |
| Job     | chef | paramedic        | teacher  | dancer        | security-guard    |

