.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There 5 different types of food: kiwi, zucchini, spinach, cherry, peach
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, skiing, biathlon, cycling, skateboarding
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, airplane, helicopter, roller
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the malaysian and the person driving the roller##2
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is between the thai and the person driving the airplane##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the american is the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person eating cherry is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Food         | spinach    | peach  | zucchini  | kiwi      | cherry |
| Sport   | skiing    | skateboarding   | cycling | biathlon | swimming   |
| Transport   | airplane | scooter    | roller    | helicopter       | quad-bike         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 